  "title": "Xtra Spicy Jamaican Chicken Wrap",
  "description": "A pungent and snappy post-workout Jamaican dish featuring pecorino and ssam-wrap style, friendly to Buddhist temple dietary preferences",
  "cuisine": "Jamaican",
